    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is a simple solution that can be used when converting a string to a hex format:</p>\n\n<pre><code>private static String encryptPassword(String password) throws NoSuchAlgorithmException, UnsupportedEncodingException {\n\n    MessageDigest crypt = MessageDigest.getInstance(\"SHA-1\");\n    crypt.reset();\n    crypt.update(password.getBytes(\"UTF-8\"));\n\n    return new BigInteger(1, crypt.digest()).toString(16);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
