    "question_id" : 4895523,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>It is not printing correctly because you need to use Base64 encoding. With Java 8 you can encode using <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Base64.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Base64</a> encoder class.</p>\n<pre><code>public static String toSHA1(byte[] convertme) throws NoSuchAlgorithmException {\n    MessageDigest md = MessageDigest.getInstance(&quot;SHA-1&quot;);\n    return Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(md.digest(convertme));\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Result</strong></p>\n<p>This will give you your expected output of <code>5baa61e4c9b93f3f0682250b6cf8331b7ee68fd8</code></p>\n"
