    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Base 64 Representation of <code>SHA1</code> Hash:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String hashedVal = Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(DigestUtils.sha1(stringValue.getBytes(Charset.forName(\"UTF-8\"))));\n</code></pre>\n"
